node.text:
There's just something about a quokka that makes everything better 😀❤️
Rottnest Island is known worldwide to be the home of the happiest animal on earth - The Quokka. Close relatives of wallabies, these animals are found all over Rottnest Island in Australia. 🙂🇦🇺 
Video 1 & 2 by: @hobopeeba 
Slides 3-7 by: @cruzysuzy

TAG someone you'd enjoy this beautiful sunrise with! ❤️
Video by: @momentsofgregory 
Music by: Halsey - Without Me (Cover by Alex Chambers) 🎶 
Location: @discoversoneva

Welcome to Italy 🇮🇹 
Which of these places do you most want to visit? 🤍
Video 1 by: @antocadei in Tellaro
Photo 2 by: @isthatdann in Positano
Video 3 by: @sennarelax in Portofino 
Video 4 by: @gianmarco.gabriele in Venice 
Video 5 by: @markoconforti in Positano
Video 6 by: @takemyhearteverywhere at Chalet Al Foss
Video 7 by @terplanet on Amalfi Coast

Video 10 by: @sennarelax in Milan
